                    browser collection with a rough image-based grade.
                  </p>
                  <div className="rounded-2xl border border-yellow-300/20 bg-yellow-300/10 p-4 text-yellow-100">
                    Best flow: upload card → Find Likely Card → pick the best match →
                    Estimate Grade + Save.
                  </div>
                </CardContent>
              </Card>

              {matchedCard ? (
                <Card className="border-white/10 bg-slate-950/60 shadow-xl">
